At least 20 people are killed, including senior officials, in an attack on the Central Hotel in Mogadishu. (BBC)Five members of the NATO-led coalition die and five others are injured in a non-combat helicopter crash in Kabul. The Associated Press reported the chopper collided with a monitoring balloon on landing. Nationalities weren't identified by NATO's Resolute Support; the British said two were Royal Air Force personnel. (BBC) (CNN) (USA Today)